text: Geikie is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Archibald Geikie (1835–1924), Scottish geologist and writer *Georgina Geikie (born 1984), British sport shooter *James Geikie (1839–1915), Scottish geologist *John Cunningham Geikie (1824–1906), Scottish Presbyterian minister and writer *Walter Geikie (1795–1837), Scottish painter ==See also== *Geikie Gorge, Western Australia *Geikie, Alberta *Geikie River (Saskatchewan) *Mount Geikie (Canada)
title: Geikie
